commit.message:
Fix val-prof-7.c on --target_board 'unix/-m32'

	* gcc.dg/tree-prof/val-prof-7.c (int main): Change size
	of memory operations so that it can be handled by core2
	in 32-bit mode.

From-SVN: r239498
